data.description: Welcome to your new home in the charming town of Waterloo, Nebraska! Situated in a peaceful cul-de-sac. At only 2.5 years old, this delightful zero-entry ranch home offers the perfect blend of small town living with big city style. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the grandeur of vaulted ceilings, which create a sense of spaciousness throughout the main living areas. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring sleek cabinetry, quartz countertops, modern appliances, and ample counter space for meal preparation along with a large walk in pantry. This home also offers the versatility of a bonus office/den, providing the perfect space for remote work, hobbies, or unwinding with a good book. Additionally, the ready-to-finish walk-up attic presents endless possibilities for customization, whether you envision a playroom, extra bedroom, or a home gym. And with the added convenience of a low 1.7 tax levy, you can enjoy the benefits of homeownership without breaking the bank. Open Sunday 12-2
